data.description: Fully remodeled gorgeous house in the heart of Mount Holly. Fresh paint, stylish multicolor ceiling LED lights. Updated facade with board and batten siding and black windows.  New dual zone HVAC system. New water heater. New roof. New interior and exterior doors. Fully remodeled bathrooms. Premium 42" tall wooden kitchen cabinets. Stainless steel appliances. New laminate on the first floor and carpet in bedrooms and stairs.   You will find plenty of opportunities in this house.
